imdb.plot outline: Sexposed is a documentary show that explores different aspects of British sexual culture. In this first series, Sexposed looks at the British adult entertainment business. Ever wondered what it is like to work in porn? You can find out from well known, and lesser known, performers who tell their own stories in their own words.
